title: Greedy Viking2.0.4.apk
description:
Description
Play the most addictive tough game of the decade. Make ur way to the top. There is always a way. Cant find the way? Take a leap of faith...
Test how Greedy you are with Greedy Viking. How far you will go to risk your life for the beautiful sparkling Diamonds. A few Diamonds and money always helps,Show your skill in collecting diamonds.Free the Dragons sleeping in their ice cubes,let the dragon take you to the top. Break a dragon egg to grab the tail of a baby dragon which will take you up. The better your Hand Eye coordination, the higher u go.
Use your Sharp brain to analyse the coming situation and act quickly. Understand the Physics of the 3 world Grass,Ice,Rubber and act accordingly.
Make High Scores and Share your Scores with your Friends with Google+.
Play Greedy Viking and end your Boring Days.
Its all about the Greed.
